  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE HEROES</h2><br>Heroes with different elements, classes, races, abilities, and stories! Will you play with a human warrior who controls fire, or with an elf hunter who creates ice clones? And many more like this!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG ELEMENTS</h2><br>Choose your evolution stats, purchase and upgrade items, combine skills and play according to your style-whether dealing massive damage or becoming immortal. Alternatively, focus on boosting your movement speed and sprinting wildly around; that's an option too.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE THE MECHANICS</h2><br>You're in charge of all of the hero's movement and skills! Take aim and land your skills, dodge the arrows, defeat bosses and try to survive for 30 turns. Remember, avoid getting cornered, and dash is your best friend. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE HEROES</h2><br>Heroes with different elements, classes, races, abilities, and stories! Will you play with a human warrior who controls fire, or with an elf hunter who creates ice clones? And many more like this!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5f723ac0f0f71cd580c48ee1dfcb3228.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG ELEMENTS</h2><br>Choose your evolution stats, purchase and upgrade items, combine skills and play according to your style-whether dealing massive damage or becoming immortal. Alternatively, focus on boosting your movement speed and sprinting wildly around; that's an option too.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/429db82c69975fbb4c293aea08f356ac.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE THE MECHANICS</h2><br>You're in charge of all of the hero's movement and skills! Take aim and land your skills, dodge the arrows, defeat bosses and try to survive for 30 turns. Remember, avoid getting cornered, and dash is your best friend. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.poster.avif?t=1739613519\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.webm?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718470/extras/5d54df2709f5610bed368eda548ee622.mp4?t=1739613519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
